袋子。

205
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,080
Paper or plastic bags.
纸袋还是塑料袋。

206
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,080
All right.
好的。

207
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,560
