00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:27,840
Do you want paper or plastic?
你想要纸袋还是塑料袋？

209
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,840
Right.
没错。

210
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:31,840
So you can choose plastic bags or paper bags.
所以你可以选择塑料袋或纸袋。

211
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,840
Okay.
好的。

